horizontal-scaling-ratio-description:
There are a total of 5 gear, the higher the gear,
the higher the magnification when ctrl + mouse wheel zoomin
horizontal-roll-ratio-description:
There are 5 gear positions in total. The higher the gear position,
the larger the step length of the left and right sliding waveform timeline
vertical-roll-ratio-description:
There are 5 gear positions in total. The higher the gear position,
the larger the step length of the up and down sliding waveform timeline
wavecolor.normal-vec: wave of more than one width
prerender-description:
Prerendering will make rendering faster, but will take up extra memory
If your computer has more than 10 GB of memory, we recommend you turn it on.
